{
  "title": "Bouncy-QQ Zesty Venezuelan Pork Chops Skewers",
  "description": "A crowd-pleasing dish featuring marinated pork chops, grilled on a robata grill for a smoky flavor.",
  "cuisine": "venezuelan",
