  "instructions": [
    "Marinate the pork chops in a mixture of shio-koji cure, lime juice, garlic, and red pepper flakes for at least 2 hours.",
    "Thread the marinated pork onto skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
    "Brush the robata grill with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill the skewers over medium-high heat for 8-10 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before slicing and serving.",
    "Serve with chimichurri sauce and scallions on top."
  ],
